                                <h3>What about nanofat?</h3>
                                <p>
                                    Nanofat uses the same liposuction harvesting technique as fat grafting; however, the fat is processed in such a way that it has more regenerative stem cell qualities than the structural fat used as filler. This is usually injected in much smaller quantities, and can have dramatic results in overall skin quality, texture and the appearance of fine lines and wrinkles.
                                </p>
